\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af8\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f5
Aj ob\u269\'0danov zosmie\u353\'61\u328\'48ujete. Rokovanie o pet\u237\'edcii ob\u269\'0danov. Najsk\u244\'f4r vl\u225\'e1da a vl\u225\'e1dna koal\u237\'edcia vlastne presad\u237\'ed z\u225\'e1kon, ktor\u253\'fd m\u225\'e1 dopad na ob\u269\'0danov o pois\u357\'65ovniach a a\u382\'7e potom ste poslanci vl\u225\'e1dnej koal\u237\'edcie ochotn\u237\'ed rokova\u357\'65 o ich pet\u237\'edcii, ktor\u225\'e1 smeruje k tomu, aby tento z\u225\'e1kon nebol prijat\u253\'fd. Mus\u237\'edm poveda\u357\'65, \u382\'7ee vl\u225\'e1da odmieta ak\u250\'fako\u318\'3evek kritiku a doslova vulg\u225\'e1rnym sp\u244\'f4sobom patriacim do \u269\'0dias hlboko pred rokom 1989 \u250\'fato\u269\'0d\u237\'ed na slobodu m\u233\'e9di\u237\'ed.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af8\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f5
